snippet.title: TheVerveVEVO
snippet.description: ‘Urban Hymns’ - One of the seminal albums of the modern era celebrates its 20th Anniversary with new Super Deluxe CD and Vinyl Box Sets, released 1 September 2017. Available to pre-order now as part of a limited bundle here: https://theverve.lnk.to/UrbanHymns_2017YD
